rComments: She is a really friendly prof with funny and interesting lectures.  She keeps the course really straightforward and she is super approachable.  I would definitely take another course with her.
Amazing prof! Interesting lectures, approachable, fun labs, lots of opportunities to improve your grade.
this course is really interesting. The lectures are great and so are the films. the prof is friendly and approachable.

I really liked the prof.  Her lectures are really well organized and straightforward.  This course is the most interesting that I have taken so far!!! The tests are hard, but the assignments were graded fairly, and she offers a lot of help.
Prof is enthusiastic and approachable. The lectures were really interesting.  The assignments were straightforward, but the tests are hard.
interesting course, prof well organized and approachable.

She didn't portray much excitement in the material. She pretty much read her notes from front, with no effect or emotion. The essay topics were interesting, but the exam questions were darn hard! With all the negatives, I'd still recommend this course as the material was quite interesting.
yikes. nothing personal against her, but the material is hard, and she seems to be reciting the whole book during lectures. thanks, but i might as well just sit at home and read the book.
